Package: shiny.webawesome
Title: 'shiny' Bindings for 'Web Awesome' Components
Version: 1.0.0
Authors@R: 
    person("M. B.", "Anand", , "privateanand@gmail.com", role = c("aut", "cre"))
Description: Provides an 'R' and 'shiny' interface to the 'Web Awesome'
    component library. The package is generator-driven, exposing 'Web Awesome'
    web components as 'R' functions that produce HTML tags and integrate with
    the reactive model that 'shiny' uses.
URL: https://github.com/mbanand/shiny.webawesome,
    https://www.shiny-webawesome.org
BugReports: https://github.com/mbanand/shiny.webawesome/issues
License: MIT + file LICENSE
Encoding: UTF-8
